  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assemble vehicles on a realistic production line, from the chassis to the final assembly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance your cars with upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optimize your production process to work more efficiently and unlock new models.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Logistics System: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Restock car parts by driving a forklift.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Car Maintenance & Repairs: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fix vehicle issues such as scratches, check tire pressure, and ensure everything is in top condition.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build different types of vehicles:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compact</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sedan</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sport</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Electric</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assemble vehicles on a realistic production line, from the chassis to the final assembly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance your cars with upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optimize your production process to work more efficiently and unlock new models.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Logistics System: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Restock car parts by driving a forklift.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Car Maintenance & Repairs: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fix vehicle issues such as scratches, check tire pressure, and ensure everything is in top condition.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build different types of vehicles:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compact</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sedan</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sport</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Electric</p></li></ul>",
